        "TileImage": "$($repository 3ed1c7e6-7707-48b4-a0f0-b933bc851fdb).Image",
        "Description": "Claudia Di Meo is an ex-assassin for the ICA who left recently, and now works as a waiter in a sapienza mansion. She must be killed before she can leak our secrets. She appears to have also gifted this info to her brother &quot;Rocco&quot; and her friend, a local deli shop owner. Kill them all.\r\rGood luck, 47.",
